dc_title_s: Land Use (Existing and Future) Jackson County, WI 2010
dc_description_s: These data layers represent land use for Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Jackson_LandUse_2010.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Jackson_ExistingLandUse_2010' and 'Jackson_FutureLandUse_2010'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
